<li style=" font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: Palatino;">
<p><span style=" font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: Palatino;">If either the </span><span style=" font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: Courier;">fork </span><span style=" font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: Palatino;">fails or </span><span style=" font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: Courier;">waitpid </span><span style=" font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: Palatino;">returns an error other than </span><span style=" font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: Courier;">EINTR</span><span style=" font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: Palatino;">, </span><span style=" font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: Courier;">system </span><span style=" font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: Palatino;">returns </span><span style=" font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: Symbol;">−</span><span style=" font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: Palatino;">1 with </span><span style=" font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: Courier;">errno </span><span style=" font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: Palatino;">set to indicate the error.</span></p>
</li>
<li style=" font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: Palatino;">
<p><span style=" font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: Palatino;">If the </span><span style=" font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: Courier;">exec </span><span style=" font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: Palatino;">fails, implying that the shell can’t be executed, the return value is as if the shell had executed </span><span style=" font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: Courier;">exit(127)</span><span style=" font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: Palatino;">.</span></p>
</li>
<li style=" font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: Palatino;">
<p><span style=" font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: Palatino;">Otherwise, all three functions—</span><span style=" font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: Courier;">fork</span><span style=" font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: Palatino;">, </span><span style=" font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: Courier;">exec</span><span style=" font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: Palatino;">, and </span><span style=" font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: Courier;">waitpid</span><span style=" font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: Palatino;">—succeed, and the return value from </span><span style=" font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: Courier;">system </span><span style=" font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: Palatino;">is the termination status of the shell, in the format specified for </span><span style=" font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: Courier;">waitpid</span><span style=" font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: Palatino;">.</span></p>
</li>
